'''拉沃托'''（'''Larvotto'''）是[[蒙特卡洛|蒙特卡洛]]東北部的住宅区，位于[[摩纳哥公国|摩纳哥公国]]。<ref name="gouv.mc">http://www.gouv.mc/devwww/wwwnew.nsf/1909$/dfb8c2ae4774e8d9c12575ac0046c0e5gb?OpenDocument&Count=10000&InfoChap= {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110927091928/http://www.gouv.mc/devwww/wwwnew.nsf/1909%24/dfb8c2ae4774e8d9c12575ac0046c0e5gb?OpenDocument&Count=10000&InfoChap= |date=2011-09-27 }}</ref> 它是摩纳哥10个现代区（Wards）之一。<ref name="gouv.mc"/>

==人口==
摩纳哥最大的行政区（人口），按面积也是第二大（次于[[芳特维耶|芳特维耶]]）。拉沃托人口5,443 面积0.34 km². ([http://www.gouv.mc/devwww/wwwnew.nsf/1909$/dfb8c2ae4774e8d9c12575ac0046c0e5gb?OpenDocument&Count=10000&InfoChap= Census 2008] {{Wayback|url=http://www.gouv.mc/devwww/wwwnew.nsf/1909$/dfb8c2ae4774e8d9c12575ac0046c0e5gb?OpenDocument&Count=10000&InfoChap= |date=20110927091928 }}).

这里政府机构很少，不过摩纳哥唯一的会议中心在这里。 <ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.visitmonaco.com/en/Business-Meetings/Convention-Bureau |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-01-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120102215815/http://www.visitmonaco.com/en/Business-Meetings/Convention-Bureau |archivedate=2012-01-02 }}</ref>

==位置==
Larvotto位于国家的东南部，蒙特卡洛东部<ref name="visitmonaco.com">{{Cite web |url=http://www.visitmonaco.com/us/About-Monaco/Geography |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-01-03 |archive-date=2012-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120102114306/http://www.visitmonaco.com/us/About-Monaco/Geography |dead-url=no }}</ref> Larvotto通常认为是蒙特卡洛的一部分，尽管他是独立的行政区（Ward.）<ref name="visitmonaco.com"/>

==旅游==

==特色==
Larvotto是仅次于[[蒙特卡洛|蒙特卡洛]]的住宅/旅游区。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.visitmonaco.com/us/Places-to-visit/Walks |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-01-03 |archive-date=2012-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120106073322/http://www.visitmonaco.com/us/Places-to-visit/Walks |dead-url=no }}</ref> 比如，[http://www.tripadvisor.com/Hotel_Review-g190409-d229111-Reviews-Le_Meridien_Beach_Plaza-Monte_Carlo.htm Le Meridien Beach Plaza] 就位于这里<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.lemeridienmontecarlo.com/en/local-area-en |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-01-03 |archive-date=2011-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111016122408/http://www.lemeridienmontecarlo.com/en/local-area-en |dead-url=no }}</ref> Its location within Monaco makes it a easy walking detection, also because it has so many parks, many people are choosing to move here from neighboring Saint Roman and other Wards.<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.montecarlo-realestate.com/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-01-03 |archive-date=2011-08-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110810151250/http://www.montecarlo-realestate.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>
       
<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.montecarlo-realestate.com/en/quartiers/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-01-03 |archive-date=2011-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111101193429/http://www.montecarlo-realestate.com/en/quartiers |dead-url=no }}</ref> 住宅通常比临近的[[Saint_Roman,_Monaco|圣罗曼]]或 [[Saint_Michel,_Monaco|Saint Michel]]高一两成。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.montecarlo-realestate.com/en/building/19-buckingham+palace |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-01-03 |archive-date=2012-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120407071853/http://www.montecarlo-realestate.com/en/building/19-buckingham+palace |dead-url=no }}</ref>

